hammerjump|A bomb jump trick in Palace of Darkness that skips a large portion of the dungeon. Tutorial by BluntBunny here: https://www.twitch.tv/videos/170642679 (old version: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IMqqGzU_eo0)
