quickwarp|With the camera aligned to the correct horizontal pixel when initiating a mirror warp or entering a warp tile, the warp animation can be shortened by 34 frames. More info here: https://alttp-wiki.net/index.php/Quick_Warps ~ Screenshots here: https://imgur.com/a/m1e8O
